MatchedObjectDescriptor.QualificationSummary:
Your resume must demonstrate at least one year of specialized experience at or equivalent to the GS-07 grade level or pay band in the Federal service or equivalent experience in the private or public sector. Specialized experience must demonstrate the following:
-Experience performing audits on Weight Handling Equipment (WHE) to identify quality problems and opportunities for improvements;
-Experience developing/revising audit plans, train audit team members, direct audit evolutions, prepares reports and conduct follow-ups to assure corrective/preventive actions have been implemented;
-Experience using plans, statistical technique, graphs and charts to prepare and present analysis results;
-Experience conducting investigations of reported equipment/system failures to identify responsible parties, root causes and corrective actions needed to prevent recurrences;
-Experience applying knowledge of quality assurance concepts, principles and methodology in developing and implementing an effective WHE quality assurance program;
-Experience applying knowledge of WHE types, configurations and systems to facilitate WHE on-site inspections of failed systems/components and promote ease of communications with cognizant civilian and military personnel.;
-Experience using oral and written communication skills to conduct interviews, training classes and prepare clear written reports. Your resume must demonstrate at least one year of specialized experience at or equivalent to the GS-09 grade level or pay band in the Federal service or equivalent experience in the private or public sector. Specialized experience must demonstrate the following:
